text: Nodubothea zapoteca is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Monne and Monne in 2008. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz – Nodubothea zapoteca. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2008
